title: Lilly Singh
itunes:title: Lilly Singh
itunes:subtitle: Lilly Singh (Superwoman Vlogs, A Little Late with Lilly Singh, A Trip to Unicorn Island) joins Anna to discuss popcorn, slacks, prom, talk shows, infinity and foot massages. Anna and Lilly then give Unqualified advice to Lindsay and Jackie.
description:
In this episode...

- Popcorn and braids
- Boating with Conan O’Brien
- Strict parents
- Slow dancing at prom
- Lilly’s Wikipedia page
- Talk show small talk and high heels
- Anna gets a foot massage
- Dating in LA
- Writing a book
- Being the weird kid
- Advice to callers Lindsey and Jackie
